       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
      ******************************************************************
      *           I D E N T I F I C A T I O N   D I V I S I O N        *
      ******************************************************************
       PROGRAM-ID. COB06250.
      ******************************************************************
      *                                                                *
      *     Processa acumulados GALP Frota                             *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
      * Descriçăo da funcionalidade                                    *
      * - Actualiza a tabela de valores acumulados GALP Frota          *
      ******************************************************************
      *           L O G     D E     A L T E R A C O E S                *
      ******************************************************************
      *  INICIO  * AUTOR  * FIM    *  C O M E N T A R I O S            *
      *          *        *        *                                   *
      *          *        *        *                                   *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
      ******************************************************************
      *           E N V I R O N M E N T         D I V I S I O N        *
      ******************************************************************
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                     CONFIGURATION SECTION                      *
      ******************************************************************
       SOURCE-COMPUTER. IBM-AS400.
       OBJECT-COMPUTER. IBM-AS400.
       SPECIAL-NAMES.
           DECIMAL-POINT IS COMMA.
      ******************************************************************
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                      INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION                      *
      ******************************************************************
       FILE-CONTROL.
      ******************************************************************
       DATA DIVISION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                   D A T A   D I V I S I O N                    *
      ******************************************************************
       FILE SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                          FILE SECTION                          *
      ******************************************************************
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                    WORKING STORAGE SECTION                     *
      ******************************************************************
      *
      ******************************************************************
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      ******************************************************************
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD2800 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD3001 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD6702 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD7805 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.

      ******************************************************************
      * CONSTANTES
      ******************************************************************
       01  CONSTANTES.
           05 WS-PROGNAME              PIC  X(10) VALUE 'COB06300'.
           05 CON-COVT2800             PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COVT2800'.
           05 CON-COVT6702             PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COVT6702'.
           05 CON-COVT6405             PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COVT6405'.
           05 CON-COVT7805             PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COVT7805'.
           05 CON-COVT3001             PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COVT3001'.
           05 CON-GALPFROTA            PIC  X(10) VALUE 'GALPFROTA'.
           05 CON-CS-2                 PIC  X(01) VALUE '2'.
           05 CON-S                    PIC  X(01) VALUE 'S'.
           05 CON-CR                   PIC  X(02) VALUE 'CR'.
           05 CON-DATE-MIN             PIC  X(10) VALUE '0001-01-01'.
      ********* CONTAS **************
           05 CON-CTA-GALP              PIC  X(10)  VALUE 'VIA02044'   .
           05 CON-CTA-VENCIMENTO        PIC  X(10)  VALUE 'VIA01001'   .
           05 CON-CTA-SEGSOC-CB         PIC  X(10)  VALUE 'VIA13001'   .
           05 CON-CTA-IRS               PIC  X(10)  VALUE 'VIA13002'   .
           05 CON-CTA-SEGSOC-EP         PIC  X(10)  VALUE 'VIA06001'   .
           05 CON-SUBS-FERIAS           PIC  X(10)  VALUE 'VIA01002'   .
           05 CON-SUBS-NATAL            PIC  X(10)  VALUE 'VIA01003'   .
      ********* STATUS **************
           05 CON-TRANSMIT              PIC  X(02)  VALUE 'TR'.
           05 CON-INTEGRADO             PIC  X(02)  VALUE 'IN'.
           05 CON-RECEBIDO              PIC  X(02)  VALUE 'RC'.
           05 CON-ERRO                  PIC  X(02)  VALUE 'ER'.
           05 CON-PROCESSADO            PIC  X(02)  VALUE 'PR'.
      ********* ERROS ***************
           05 CON-ERR-PER-MULT          PIC  X(03)  VALUE '001'.
           05 CON-ERR-IDFOR-NOTFND      PIC  X(03)  VALUE '002'.
           05 CON-ERR-IDFOR-MULT        PIC  X(03)  VALUE '003'.
           05 CON-ERR-IDINV-NOTFND      PIC  X(03)  VALUE '004'.
           05 CON-ERR-AMOUNT-INV        PIC  X(03)  VALUE '005'.
           05 CON-ERR-STAT-INV          PIC  X(03)  VALUE '006'.
           05 CON-ERR-VALOR-INV         PIC  X(03)  VALUE '007'.
           05 CON-ERR-MULT-INV          PIC  X(03)  VALUE '008'.
           05 CON-ERR-MARG-INV          PIC  X(03)  VALUE '009'.
           05 CON-ERR-STAT-PAG          PIC  X(03)  VALUE '010'.
      ********* STATUS DATA *********
           05 CON-ACTIVO                PIC  X(01)  VALUE 'A'.

      ********* MARGEM **************
           05 WS-VALOR-MAX     PIC S9(11)V9(2) COMP-3 VALUE ZEROES.
           05 WS-VALOR-MIN     PIC S9(11)V9(2) COMP-3 VALUE ZEROES.
           05 WS-MARGEM        PIC S9(11)V9(2) COMP-3 VALUE ZEROES.
           05 WS-PERCENT       PIC S9(11)V9(2) COMP-3 VALUE ZEROES.
      *

      ******************************************************************
      * VARIAVEIS
      ******************************************************************
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-CSTATUS                PIC  X(02)  VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-CERRO                  PIC  X(03)  VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-DATA-SEARCH            PIC  X(10)  VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-DATA-MINIMA            PIC  X(10)  VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-DATA-HOJE              PIC  X(10)  VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-NSEQ                   PIC S9(10)  COMP-3 VALUE ZEROES.

           05 WS-ANO-PER-WRK               PIC  9(04).
           05 WS-MES-PER-WRK               PIC  9(02).

           05 WS-YEAR                      PIC  X(04).
           05 WS-MONTH                     PIC  X(02).

           05 WS-DATA-PROC                 PIC  X(10).
      ******************************************************************
      *  SWITCH
      ******************************************************************
       01  WS-SWITCHES.
           05 WS-STATUS-COT78       PIC S9(03) VALUE 0.
              88 WS-COT78-OK                   VALUE 0.
              88 WS-COT78-NOTFND               VALUE 100.

           05 SW-FILE               PIC S9(01) VALUE 0.
              88 SW-FILE-OK                    VALUE 0.
              88 SW-FILE-NOK                   VALUE 1.

      ******************************************************************
      * COPYS
      ******************************************************************
           COPY AQCL0001.
           COPY AQCW0109.
           COPY VIAL0015.
           COPY VIAW0011.
           COPY VIAW0012.
           COPY VIATK001.
           COPY VIATK002.
           COPY COCK0002.
           COPY COCK0001.
           COPY COCF3100.
           COPY VIAL1000.
           COPY COCL0250.
           COPY COCL0255.

      ******************************************************************
      * DB2
      ******************************************************************
       01  WS-CURSOR-VARS.
           05 FILLER                     PIC X(01) VALUE SPACES.

      *
      * MOVIMENTOS FACTURA GALP FROTA
      *
           EXEC SQL
                DECLARE COT78 CURSOR FOR
                SELECT   DISTINCT CPERIOD
                                , GCLIENTE
                                , NIDPROJECTO
                 FROM COVT7805
                 WHERE CSTATUS <> "PR"
                 ORDER BY CPERIOD
                        , GCLIENTE
           END-EXEC.

      ******************************************************************
       01  FILLER              PIC X(40) VALUE 'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE'.
      ******************************************************************
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                        LINKAGE SECTION                         *
      ******************************************************************
           COPY AQCW0009.
      ******************************************************************
       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING AQCW0009-DATA.
      ******************************************************************
      *              P R O C E D U R E   D I V I S I O N               *
      ******************************************************************
       0000-MAINLINE.
      ******************************************************************
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
                 THRU 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 3000-FIM-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3000-FIM-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

       0000-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           GOBACK.

      ******************************************************************
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA'      TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM AQCP0100-REG-INICIO
                 THRU AQCP0100-REG-INICIO-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM AQCP0100-OBT-DADOS-ARQ
                 THRU AQCP0100-OBT-DADOS-ARQ-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              MOVE AQCW0100-AT-DTOP         TO AQCW0005-DT98
              PERFORM AQCP0005-CONV-DT8INDT10
                 THRU AQCP0005-CONV-DT8INDT10-EXIT
              MOVE AQCW0005-DTX10           TO WS-DATA-PROC
           END-IF.

       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA'        TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-OPEN-CURSOR
                 THRU 2200-OPEN-CURSOR-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2300-FETCH-CURSOR
                 THRU 2300-FETCH-CURSOR-EXIT

              PERFORM 2400-PROC-CURSOR
                 THRU 2400-PROC-CURSOR-EXIT
                      UNTIL NOT DB2-OK
                         OR NOT AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS

              EXEC SQL
                   CLOSE COT78
              END-EXEC
           END-IF.

       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2200-OPEN-CURSOR.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2200-OPEN-CURSOR'          TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE DCLCOCD7805.

           EXEC SQL
                OPEN COT78
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT7805        TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN DB2-OK
                CONTINUE
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2200-OPEN-CURSOR-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2300-FETCH-CURSOR.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2300-FETCH-CURSOR'         TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
              FETCH  COT78
               INTO
                    :COCD7805-CPERIOD
                  , :COCD7805-GCLIENTE
                  , :COCD7805-NIDPROJECTO
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT7805        TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN DB2-OK
           WHEN DB2-NOTFND
                CONTINUE
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2300-FETCH-CURSOR-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2400-PROC-CURSOR.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2400-PROC-CURSOR'          TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              SET SW-FILE-NOK TO TRUE
              PERFORM 2680-VAL-FICH
                 THRU 2680-VAL-FICH-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
             IF SW-FILE-OK
               PERFORM 2680-OBT-STATUS-PROC
                  THRU 2680-OBT-STATUS-PROC-EXIT
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
             IF SW-FILE-OK
               PERFORM 2500-OBT-RECORD
                  THRU 2500-OBT-RECORD-EXIT
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
             IF SW-FILE-OK
               IF COCD7805-NIDINVOICE EQUAL ZEROES
                 PERFORM 2500-OBT-INVOICE
                    THRU 2500-OBT-INVOICE-EXIT
               ELSE
                 PERFORM 2500-OBT-INVOICE-2
                    THRU 2500-OBT-INVOICE-2-EXIT
               END-IF
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
             IF SW-FILE-OK
               IF COCD7805-CSTATUS NOT EQUAL WS-CSTATUS OR
                  COCD7805-CERRO   NOT EQUAL WS-CERRO
                 PERFORM 2500-UPD-RECORD
                    THRU 2500-UPD-RECORD-EXIT
               END-IF
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
             IF SW-FILE-OK
               IF (COCD6702-CSTATUS = COCK0002-CSTATDP-ORCM OR
                   COCD6702-CSTATUS = COCK0002-CSTATDP-RECB)
                 PERFORM 2695-CALCULA-TOTAIS
                    THRU 2695-CALCULA-TOTAIS-EXIT
               END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
             IF SW-FILE-OK
               IF (COCD6702-CSTATUS = COCK0002-CSTATDP-ORCM OR
                   COCD6702-CSTATUS = COCK0002-CSTATDP-RECB)
                 PERFORM 2510-TRATA-PAG
                    THRU 2510-TRATA-PAG-EXIT
               END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2300-FETCH-CURSOR
                 THRU 2300-FETCH-CURSOR-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2400-PROC-CURSOR-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2500-OBT-INVOICE.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2500-OBT-INVOICE'       TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE DCLCOCD6702           REPLACING NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                                 ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES


           MOVE ZEROES                 TO COCD6702-NIDINVOICE
           MOVE ZEROES                 TO COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT
           MOVE SPACES                 TO COCD6702-CSTATUS
           MOVE COCD7805-NIDPROJECTO   TO COCD6702-NIDPROJECTO
           MOVE COCD7805-GCLIENTE      TO COCD6702-GCLIENTE
           MOVE COCD7805-CPERIOD       TO WS-YEAR
           MOVE COCD7805-CPERIOD(6:2)  TO WS-MONTH

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT  NIDINVOICE
                     ,  NTOTALAMOUNT
                     ,  CSTATUS
                  INTO :COCD6702-NIDINVOICE
                     , :COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT
                     , :COCD6702-CSTATUS
                  FROM  COVT6702_EXPENSES
                 WHERE GCLIENTE          = :COCD6702-GCLIENTE
                   AND NIDPROJECTO       = :COCD6702-NIDPROJECTO
                   AND YEAR(DDATAEMISS)  = :WS-YEAR
                   AND MONTH(DDATAEMISS) = :WS-MONTH
                   AND CSTATUS          <> "04"
                   AND GREFINV           = :COCD6702-GREFINV
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT6702           TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN DB2-OK
             IF (COCD6702-CSTATUS = COCK0002-CSTATDP-ORCM OR
                 COCD6702-CSTATUS = COCK0002-CSTATDP-RECB)
               IF COCD7805-NIDINVOICE NOT EQUAL COCD6702-NIDINVOICE
                 MOVE COCD6702-NIDINVOICE   TO COCD7805-NIDINVOICE
                 MOVE COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT TO COCD7805-NTOTALAMOUNT
               END-IF
               IF COCD6702-CSTATUS = COCK0002-CSTATDP-RECB
                  MOVE CON-RECEBIDO       TO WS-CSTATUS
               ELSE
                 MOVE CON-INTEGRADO           TO WS-CSTATUS
               END-IF
               MOVE SPACES                  TO COCD7805-CERRO
             END-IF
             IF COCD6702-CSTATUS = COCK0002-CSTATDP-PAG
               IF COCD7805-NIDINVOICE NOT EQUAL COCD6702-NIDINVOICE
                 MOVE COCD6702-NIDINVOICE   TO COCD7805-NIDINVOICE
                 MOVE COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT TO COCD7805-NTOTALAMOUNT
               END-IF
               MOVE CON-PROCESSADO        TO WS-CSTATUS
               MOVE CON-ERR-STAT-PAG      TO COCD7805-CERRO
             END-IF
           WHEN DB2-NOTFND
             MOVE ZEROES                    TO COCD7805-NIDINVOICE
             MOVE ZEROES                    TO COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT
             MOVE SPACES                    TO COCD6702-CSTATUS
             MOVE CON-ERRO                  TO WS-CSTATUS
             MOVE CON-ERR-IDINV-NOTFND      TO COCD7805-CERRO
           WHEN DB2-DUPLINE
             MOVE ZEROES                    TO COCD7805-NIDINVOICE
             MOVE ZEROES                    TO COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT
             MOVE SPACES                    TO COCD6702-CSTATUS
             MOVE CON-ERRO                  TO WS-CSTATUS
             MOVE CON-ERR-MULT-INV          TO COCD7805-CERRO
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE

                MOVE COCD6702-GCLIENTE      TO AQCW0100-DESC1(1:)
                MOVE COCD6702-NIDPROJECTO   TO AQCW0100-DESC1(4:)
                MOVE COCD6702-GREFINV       TO AQCW0100-DESC1(13:)

                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2500-OBT-INVOICE-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2500-OBT-INVOICE-2.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2500-OBT-INVOICE-2'       TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE DCLCOCD6702           REPLACING NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                                 ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES


           MOVE ZEROES                 TO COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT
           MOVE SPACES                 TO COCD6702-CSTATUS
           MOVE SPACES                 TO COCD6702-GREFINV
           MOVE COCD7805-NIDINVOICE    TO COCD6702-NIDINVOICE
           MOVE COCD7805-NIDPROJECTO   TO COCD6702-NIDPROJECTO
           MOVE COCD7805-GCLIENTE      TO COCD6702-GCLIENTE

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT  NIDINVOICE
                     ,  NTOTALAMOUNT
                     ,  CSTATUS
                  INTO :COCD6702-NIDINVOICE
                     , :COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT
                     , :COCD6702-CSTATUS
                  FROM  COVT6702_EXPENSES
                 WHERE GCLIENTE          = :COCD6702-GCLIENTE
                   AND NIDPROJECTO       = :COCD6702-NIDPROJECTO
                   AND NIDINVOICE        = :COCD6702-NIDINVOICE
                   AND CSTATUS          <> "04"
                   AND GREFINV           = :COCD6702-GREFINV
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT6702           TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN DB2-OK
             IF (COCD6702-CSTATUS = COCK0002-CSTATDP-ORCM OR
                 COCD6702-CSTATUS = COCK0002-CSTATDP-RECB)
               IF COCD7805-NIDINVOICE NOT EQUAL COCD6702-NIDINVOICE
                 MOVE COCD6702-NIDINVOICE   TO COCD7805-NIDINVOICE
                 MOVE COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT TO COCD7805-NTOTALAMOUNT
               END-IF
               MOVE CON-INTEGRADO           TO WS-CSTATUS
               MOVE SPACES                  TO COCD7805-CERRO
             END-IF
             IF COCD6702-CSTATUS = COCK0002-CSTATDP-PAG
               MOVE COCD6702-NIDINVOICE   TO COCD7805-NIDINVOICE
               MOVE COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT TO COCD7805-NTOTALAMOUNT
               MOVE CON-PROCESSADO        TO WS-CSTATUS
               MOVE CON-ERR-STAT-PAG      TO COCD7805-CERRO
             END-IF
           WHEN DB2-NOTFND
             MOVE ZEROES                    TO COCD7805-NIDINVOICE
             MOVE ZEROES                    TO COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT
             MOVE SPACES                    TO COCD6702-CSTATUS
             MOVE CON-ERRO                  TO WS-CSTATUS
             MOVE CON-ERR-IDINV-NOTFND      TO COCD7805-CERRO
           WHEN DB2-DUPLINE
             MOVE ZEROES                    TO COCD7805-NIDINVOICE
             MOVE ZEROES                    TO COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT
             MOVE SPACES                    TO COCD6702-CSTATUS
             MOVE CON-ERRO                  TO WS-CSTATUS
             MOVE CON-ERR-MULT-INV          TO COCD7805-CERRO
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE

                MOVE COCD6702-GCLIENTE      TO AQCW0100-DESC1(1:)
                MOVE COCD6702-NIDPROJECTO   TO AQCW0100-DESC1(4:)
                MOVE COCD6702-GREFINV       TO AQCW0100-DESC1(13:)

                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2500-OBT-INVOICE-2-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2500-OBT-RECORD.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2500-OBT-RECORD'       TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE ZEROES                 TO COCD7805-NIDINVOICE
           MOVE ZEROES                 TO COCD7805-NTOTALAMOUNT
           MOVE SPACES                 TO COCD7805-CSTATUS
           MOVE SPACES                 TO COCD7805-CERRO
           MOVE COCD7805-CSTATUS       TO WS-CSTATUS
           MOVE COCD7805-CERRO         TO WS-CERRO

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT  NIDINVOICE
                     ,  NTOTALAMOUNT
                     ,  CSTATUS
                     ,  CERRO
                     ,  IDFICH
                  INTO :COCD7805-NIDINVOICE
                     , :COCD7805-NTOTALAMOUNT
                     , :COCD7805-CSTATUS
                     , :COCD7805-CERRO
                     , :COCD7805-IDFICH
                  FROM  COVT7805
                 WHERE CPERIOD           = :COCD7805-CPERIOD
                   AND GCLIENTE          = :COCD7805-GCLIENTE
                   AND NIDPROJECTO       = :COCD7805-NIDPROJECTO
                 FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT7805           TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN DB2-OK
             CONTINUE
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE

                MOVE COCD7805-GCLIENTE      TO AQCW0100-DESC1(1:)
                MOVE COCD7805-NIDPROJECTO   TO AQCW0100-DESC1(4:)
                MOVE COCD7805-CPERIOD       TO AQCW0100-DESC1(13:)

                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2500-OBT-RECORD-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2500-UPD-RECORD.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2500-UPD-RECORD'       TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE WS-PROGNAME              TO COCD7805-CUSERID

           MOVE WS-CSTATUS          TO COCD7805-CSTATUS
           MOVE WS-CERRO            TO COCD7805-CERRO

           IF COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT NOT EQUAL ZEROES AND
              COCD7805-NTOTALAMOUNT EQUAL ZEROES
             MOVE COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT TO COCD7805-NTOTALAMOUNT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
                UPDATE COVT7805
                   SET CSTATUS      = :COCD7805-CSTATUS
                     , CERRO        = :COCD7805-CERRO
                     , NTOTALAMOUNT = :COCD7805-NTOTALAMOUNT
                     , NIDINVOICE   = :COCD7805-NIDINVOICE
                     , CUSERID      = :COCD7805-CUSERID
                     , HTIMEST      = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
                 WHERE CPERIOD     = :COCD7805-CPERIOD
                   AND GCLIENTE    = :COCD7805-GCLIENTE
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT7805               TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN DB2-OK
                    CONTINUE
               WHEN OTHER
                    SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                    MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                    MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                    MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                    MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                    PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                       THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2500-UPD-RECORD-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2510-TRATA-PAG.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2510-TRATA-PAG'           TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCD6702-CSTATUS = COCK0002-CSTATDP-ORCM
               PERFORM 2695-RECEBIMENTO
                  THRU 2695-RECEBIMENTO-EXIT
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCD3001-ISTATUS = CON-ACTIVO AND
                COCD6702-CSTATUS = COCK0002-CSTATDP-RECB
               PERFORM 2700-PAGAMENTO
                  THRU 2700-PAGAMENTO-EXIT
             END-IF
           END-IF.

       2510-TRATA-PAG-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2695-RECEBIMENTO.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2695-RECEBIMENTO    '   TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
             MOVE COCD7805-GCLIENTE       TO COCL0255-GCLIENTE
             MOVE COCD7805-NIDPROJECTO    TO COCL0255-NIDPROJECTO
             MOVE COCD7805-NIDINVOICE     TO COCL0255-NIDINVOICE
             MOVE COCD7805-MVALORLIQ      TO COCL0255-MVALOR
             MOVE COCD3001-DPAG           TO COCL0255-DDATEDUE
             SET COCL0255-GALPFROTA       TO TRUE
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCD7805-CSTATUS = CON-INTEGRADO
           AND COCD7805-CERRO = SPACES

             PERFORM ETCP0003-STD-INIT
                THRU ETCP0003-STD-INIT-EXIT

             PERFORM COCP0255-CALL-ROTINA
                THRU COCP0255-CALL-ROTINA-EXIT

             PERFORM ETCP0003-STD-END
                THRU ETCP0003-STD-END-EXIT

             IF NOT ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
               SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
               MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
               MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
               PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                  THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCD7805-CSTATUS = CON-INTEGRADO
           AND COCD7805-CERRO = SPACES
             MOVE CON-RECEBIDO               TO COCD7805-CSTATUS
             MOVE SPACES                     TO COCD7805-CERRO
             MOVE COCK0002-CSTATDP-RECB      TO COCD6702-CSTATUS
             PERFORM 2650-UPD-STATUS
                THRU 2650-UPD-STATUS-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2695-RECEBIMENTO-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2700-PAGAMENTO.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2700-PAGAMENTO      '   TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
             MOVE COCD7805-NIDINVOICE     TO COCL0250-NIDINVOICE
             MOVE COCD7805-GCLIENTE       TO COCL0250-GCLIENTE
             MOVE COCD7805-NIDPROJECTO    TO COCL0250-NIDPROJECTO
             MOVE COCD7805-MVALORLIQ      TO COCL0250-MVALOR
             MOVE COCD3001-DPAG           TO COCL0250-DPAG
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
           AND (COCD7805-CSTATUS = CON-RECEBIDO
            OR  COCD7805-CSTATUS = CON-INTEGRADO)
           AND COCD7805-CERRO = SPACES
           AND (COCD3001-DPAG = ETCL0002-DATA-PROCESSO
            OR  COCD3001-DPAG < ETCL0002-DATA-PROCESSO)
           AND COCD3001-ISTATUS = CON-ACTIVO

             PERFORM ETCP0003-STD-INIT
                THRU ETCP0003-STD-INIT-EXIT

             PERFORM COCP0250-CALL-ROTINA
                THRU COCP0250-CALL-ROTINA-EXIT

             PERFORM ETCP0003-STD-END
                THRU ETCP0003-STD-END-EXIT

             IF NOT ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
               SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
               MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
               MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
               PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                  THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
           AND (COCD7805-CSTATUS = CON-RECEBIDO
            OR  COCD7805-CSTATUS = CON-INTEGRADO)
           AND COCD7805-CERRO = SPACES
           AND (COCD3001-DPAG = ETCL0002-DATA-PROCESSO
            OR  COCD3001-DPAG < ETCL0002-DATA-PROCESSO)
           AND COCD3001-ISTATUS = CON-ACTIVO

             MOVE CON-PROCESSADO             TO COCD7805-CSTATUS
             MOVE SPACES                     TO COCD7805-CERRO
             PERFORM 2650-UPD-STATUS
                THRU 2650-UPD-STATUS-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2700-PAGAMENTO-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2650-UPD-STATUS.
      ******************************************************************

           MOVE '2650-UPD-STATUS     '   TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE WS-PROGNAME              TO COCD7805-CUSERID

           EXEC SQL
                UPDATE COVT7805
                   SET CSTATUS      = :COCD7805-CSTATUS
                     , CERRO        = :COCD7805-CERRO
                     , CUSERID      = :COCD7805-CUSERID
                     , HTIMEST      = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
      **R        WHERE IDFICH      = :COCD7805-IDFICH
                 WHERE GCLIENTE    = :COCD7805-GCLIENTE
                   AND CPERIOD     = :COCD7805-CPERIOD
      **R          AND NIDPROJECTO = :COCD7805-NIDPROJECTO
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT7805               TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN DB2-OK
                    CONTINUE
               WHEN OTHER
                    SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                    MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                    MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                    MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                    MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                    PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                       THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2650-UPD-STATUS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2680-OBT-STATUS-PROC.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2680-OBT-STATUS-PROC'   TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           MOVE COCD7805-CPERIOD           TO COCD3001-CPERIOD
           MOVE CON-CTA-GALP               TO COCD3001-NIDPROJECTO

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT DPAG
                     , ISTATUS
                  INTO :COCD3001-DPAG
                     , :COCD3001-ISTATUS
                  FROM COVT3001_PARMVENC
                 WHERE CPERIOD     = :COCD3001-CPERIOD
                   AND NIDPROJECTO = :COCD3001-NIDPROJECTO
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT3001               TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN DB2-OK
                 IF COCD3001-DPAG < WS-DATA-PROC OR
                    COCD3001-DPAG = WS-DATA-PROC
                   CONTINUE
                 ELSE
                   SET SW-FILE-NOK TO TRUE
                 END-IF
               WHEN OTHER
                    SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                    MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                    MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                    MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                    MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                    PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                       THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2680-OBT-STATUS-PROC-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2680-VAL-FICH.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2680-VAL-FICH'            TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           MOVE CON-GALPFROTA              TO COCD2800-CFILETYP
           MOVE COCD7805-CPERIOD           TO COCD2800-CCHAVE

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT CFILEIBM
                  INTO :COCD2800-CFILEIBM
                  FROM COVT2800_FILEADM
                 WHERE CFILETYP             = :COCD2800-CFILETYP
                   AND SUBSTR(CCHAVE, 1, 7) = :COCD2800-CCHAVE
                   AND STATE               <> "E"
                 FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT2800               TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN DB2-OK
                    SET SW-FILE-OK TO TRUE
               WHEN DB2-NOTFND
                    CONTINUE
               WHEN OTHER
                    SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                    MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                    MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                    MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                    MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                    PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                       THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2680-VAL-FICH-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2695-CALCULA-TOTAIS.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2695-CALCULA-TOTAIS  '    TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCD6702-CSTATUS = COCK0002-CSTATDP-ORCM
               PERFORM 2696-VALIDA-STATUS
                  THRU 2696-VALIDA-STATUS-EXIT
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCD6702-CSTATUS = COCK0002-CSTATDP-ORCM OR
                COCD6702-CSTATUS = COCK0002-CSTATDP-RECB
               PERFORM 2696-SUM-TOTAL
                  THRU 2696-SUM-TOTAL-EXIT
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF ETCL0002-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2695-CALCULA-TOTAIS-EXIT  ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'COCD7805-CIDEMP      ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (1)
              MOVE  COCD7805-CIDEMP        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'COCD7805-NIDPROJECTO ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (2)
              MOVE  COCD7805-NIDPROJECTO   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              MOVE 'WS-VALOR-MAX     '     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (4)
              MOVE  WS-VALOR-MAX           TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(4)
              MOVE 'WS-VALOR-MIN     '     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (5)
              MOVE  WS-VALOR-MIN           TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(5)
              MOVE 'COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (6)
              MOVE  COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(6)
              MOVE 'COCD7805-MVALORLIQ   ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (7)
              MOVE  COCD7805-MVALORLIQ     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(7)
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2695-CALCULA-TOTAIS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2696-VALIDA-STATUS.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2696-VALIDA-STATUS   '     TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.


       2696-VALIDA-STATUS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2696-SUM-TOTAL.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2696-SUM-TOTAL   '         TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
              SELECT IFNULL(SUM(MVALORLIQ), 0)
                INTO :COCD7805-MVALORLIQ
                FROM COVT7805
               WHERE CPERIOD        = :COCD7805-CPERIOD
                 AND GCLIENTE       = :COCD7805-GCLIENTE
                 AND NIDPROJECTO    = :COCD7805-NIDPROJECTO
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT7805        TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN DB2-OK
             CONTINUE
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2696-SUM-TOTAL-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       3000-FIM-PROGRAMA.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '3000-FIM-PROGRAMA'         TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      * Processos finais
            PERFORM AQCP0009-TRATA-RCODE
               THRU AQCP0009-TRATA-RCODE-EXIT.

            PERFORM AQCP0002-TRATA-SYNCPOINT
               THRU AQCP0002-TRATA-SYNCPOINT-EXIT.

           PERFORM AQCP0100-REG-FIM
              THRU AQCP0100-REG-FIM-EXIT.

       3000-FIM-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE AQCP0002 END-EXEC.
      ******************************************************************
           COPY AQCP0009.
           COPY AQCP0109.
           COPY VIAP0012.
           COPY VIAP0015.
           COPY VIAP1000.
           COPY COCP0250.
           COPY COCP0255.
      ******************************************************************
